  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate antihypertensive effect and safety of CS-3150 compared to Eplerenone in patients
      with essential hypertension.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Primary objective is to evaluate antihypertensive effect and safety of CS-3150 2.5 mg
      compared to Eplerenone in patients with essential hypertension.

      Secondary objective is to evaluate antihypertensive effect and safety of CS-3150 5.0 mg
      compared to 2.5 mg.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
